by magnusnordlander at 2013-10-20T14:02:39Z

According to [RFC 6648](http://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc6648), the practice of prefixing custom headers with "X-" is deprecated. I'd suggest using Debug-Token-Link as the header name instead (even though it's inconsistent with X-Debug-Token).

